ding/trailing \"HEARTBEAT_OK\" as a heartbeat ack (and may discard it).\n\nIf something needs attention, do NOT include \"HEARTBEAT_OK\"; reply with the alert text instead.\n\n# Runtime\n\nReasoning: off (hidden unless on/stream). Toggle /reasoning; /status shows Reasoning when enabled.\n\n## Documentation\n\n## Reactions\n# Reactions\n\n## Reasoning Format\n# Reasoning Format\n\n```"},"rawResponse":{"id":"0609a10fc8ccc0b00266cdbeb91398be","content":"","usage":{"input_tokens":477,"output_tokens":143,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":11773},"stop_reason":"tool_use"},"id":"llm_mmvtxptw_rsjxc6r","timestamp":1773825554948}
